      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves conditional logic, subqueries, and joins, which add to its complexity. The use of "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ROW_NUMBER()",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and conditional checks for status determination also contribute to its medium complexity level."
        }
      ]
    },
